@startuml
package "LunaSleep AI System" {
  [User] as user
  [Web Browser] as browser

  package "Frontend" {
    [Landing Page] as landing
    [Dashboard] as dashboard
    [Predictor] as predictor
    [Monitor] as monitor
    [AI Chat] as chat
    [Authentication] as auth
  }

  package "Backend" {
    [Flask App] as flask
    [API Routes] as api
    [Authentication System] as auth_sys
    [ML Predictor] as ml
    [AI Assistant] as ai
    [Sensor Monitor] as sensor
  }

  package "Database" {
    [User Model] as user_model
    [Prediction History] as pred_hist
    [Chat Sessions] as chat_sess
    [Chat Messages] as chat_msg
  }

  package "External Systems" {
    [NVIDIA NIM API] as nim
  }
}

user --> browser
browser --> landing
browser --> dashboard
browser --> predictor
browser --> monitor
browser --> chat
browser --> auth

landing --> flask
dashboard --> flask
predictor --> flask
monitor --> flask
chat --> flask
auth --> flask

flask --> api
api --> auth_sys
api --> ml
api --> ai
api --> sensor

auth_sys --> user_model
auth_sys --> pred_hist
auth_sys --> chat_sess
auth_sys --> chat_msg

ml --> api
ai --> nim
sensor --> api

user_model --> Database
pred_hist --> Database
chat_sess --> Database
chat_msg --> Database

flask --> Database

note right of flask
  Flask Application with:
  - Flask-Login for authentication
  - Flask-SQLAlchemy for database
  - Flask-SocketIO for real-time monitoring
  - HTMX for dynamic UI updates
end note

note right of ml
  XGBoost model for sleep efficiency prediction
  - Uses scikit-learn preprocessing
  - Feature importance: Age, Gender, Sleep duration,
    REM/Deep/Light sleep %, Awakenings,
    Caffeine/Alcohol consumption, Smoking status,
    Exercise frequency
end note

note right of ai
  AI Assistant using NVIDIA NIM API
  - Context-aware sleep coaching
  - Personalized recommendations
  - Chat session management
end note

note right of sensor
  Real-time sensor monitoring
  - MPU6050 accelerometer data
  - Data simulation mode
  - External sensor data support
end note

note right of nim
  NVIDIA Inference Microservice API
  - LLM inference for chat
  - Daily tips generation
end note

Database : SQLite for user data
Database : Authentication storage
Database : Prediction history
Database : Chat conversations